    },
    {
      "id": "698f9feb0000000000bfda83",
      "text": " スノボ男子、フィギュア男子観た、感動した",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771020266,
      "updated": 1771020416
    },
    {
      "id": "698fa60d0000000000485253",
      "text": "  日本勢メダル獲りすぎィ！",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771021836,
      "updated": 1771021848
    },
    {
      "id": "698fa01e0000000000bfda84",
      "text": "  フィギュアは最後まさかの波乱展開",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771020317,
      "updated": 1771020432
    },
    {
      "id": "698fa39e0000000000485251",
      "text": "  カザフスタンフィギュア初金メダルおめでとう",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771021213,
      "updated": 1771021223
    },
    {
      "id": "698fa3a90000000000485252",
      "text": "  [佐藤駿]の初々しさと[鍵山優真]の余裕さの対比がおもろい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771021225,
      "updated": 1771094086
    },
    {
      "id": "698ff33200000000002ed74b",
      "text": "  帰ったらスノボ見よう[takker.icon][caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771041586,
      "updated": 1771053490
    },
    {
      "id": "698f52431280f0000000d62e8e",
